## Project Setup

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/k8s-gpu-workload-enhancer.git
cd k8s-gpu-workload-enhancer
```

### 2. Create Python Virtual Environment

```bash
# Create venv
python3 -m venv venv

# Activate venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Verify activation (should show venv in shell prompt)
which python
```

### 3. Install Dependencies

```bash
# Install PULSAR and dependencies
pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel
pip install -e .

# Or install directly from requirements.txt
pip install -r src/pulsar/requirements.txt

# Install development dependencies (optional, for testing)
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### 4. Verify Installation

```bash
# Check Python packages
pip list

# Test PULSAR CLI
pulsar --help
```

