## API

The REST API is fully documented with Swagger/OpenAPI at `/docs` when the server is running.

### Base URL

```
http://localhost:8080
```

### Key Endpoints

#### Dashboard & UI

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `GET /` | Web dashboard |
| `GET /docs` | API documentation (Swagger UI) |
| `GET /redoc` | API documentation (ReDoc) |

#### Job Management

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Example |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/jobs` | Submit a job | `{"user": "team-a", "gpus": 4, "priority": "NORMAL"}` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/jobs` | List all jobs | Filter: `?user=team-a&status=RUNNING` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/jobs/{id}` | Get job details | Returns full job state |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/jobs/{id}` | Cancel a job | Stops job immediately |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/jobs/{id}/complete` | Mark job completed | Updates job status |

#### Cluster Status

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/cluster` | Cluster capacity and utilization |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/queues` | Queue depths per user |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/cluster/topology` | GPU topology and node info |

#### Quotas & Fairness

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/quotas` | List all quota allocations |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/quotas/{user}` | Update user quota |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/fairness` | Fairness report + Jain's index |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/fairness/allocation` | Per-team GPU allocation |

#### Monitoring

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/metrics` | Prometheus-format metrics |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/events` | Event log |

#### Health Checks

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/healthz` | Liveness probe |
| `GET` | `/readyz` | Readiness probe |

### Example API Calls

**Submit a job:**

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "user": "team-a",
    "gpus": 4,
    "priority": "NORMAL"
  }'
```

**List jobs:**

```bash
curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs?user=team-a&status=RUNNING
```

