```bash
curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cluster
```

**Get fairness metrics:**

```bash
curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fairness
```

**Prometheus metrics:**

```bash
curl http://localhost:8080/api/v1/metrics
```

