## Project Structure

The project is organized as follows:

```
.
├── src/
│   ├── pulsar/                    # PULSAR control plane (Python)
│   │   ├── types.py               # GPUJob, UserQuota, JobStatus, JobPriority
│   │   ├── queue_manager.py       # Per-user FIFO queues, policy-based dequeuing
│   │   ├── fair_scheduler.py      # Weighted fair share, Jain's index calculation
│   │   ├── admission_controller.py # Cluster capacity + per-user quota enforcement
│   │   ├── preemption.py          # Priority-based victim selection
│   │   ├── executor.py            # Creates K8s Jobs (or standalone mode)
│   │   ├── persistence.py         # SQLite job store with query builders
│   │   ├── control_plane.py       # Orchestrator (wires everything together)
│   │   ├── api_server.py          # FastAPI REST API endpoints
│   │   ├── cli.py                 # Command-line interface
│   │   ├── dashboard.py           # HTML dashboard (modular renderers)
│   │   ├── metrics.py             # Prometheus-format metrics exporter
│   │   ├── config.py              # YAML config loader + validators
│   │   ├── k8s_integration.py     # CRD definitions, K8s client helpers
│   │   ├── pulsar.yaml            # Default configuration file
│   │   └── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
│   ├── scheduler/                 # Go scheduler (KGWE)
│   │   ├── scheduler.go
│   │   ├── extender.go
│   │   └── types.go
│   ├── optimizer/                 # Python ML optimizer
│   ├── discovery/                 # Go GPU discovery service
│   ├── monitoring/                # Go Prometheus exporter
│   └── api/                       # Go API layer
│
├── deploy/
